        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "二黄正板",
          "musical_style": "二黄正板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "刽子手提刀吓煞人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "二黄正板",
          "musical_style": "二黄正板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我是那张浪子的大娘亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "二黄正板",
          "musical_style": "二黄正板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "望将爷在上容我禀"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "二黄正板",
          "musical_style": "二黄正板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "在法场哭坏了王氏女"
        },
        {
          "character": "王清天",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传话出去：有亲探亲，有故探故，少时大炮一响，人头落地。亲故就不能相见"
        },
        {
          "character": "王清天",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二刽子手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传话出去：有亲探亲，有故探故，少时大炮一响，人头落地。亲故就不能相见"
        },
        {
          "character": "二刽子手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "二黄正板",
          "musical_style": "二黄正板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "大老爷开了那天地之恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "法场上好一比森罗宝殿，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "监斩官好一比五殿闫君。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "众犯人好一比死去猪羊，一个个等候时辰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "众犯人在法场无有其数，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "寻不着浪子小姣生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "这江洋大盗吓煞人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我的儿受绑缚叫娘心痛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿在法场之上，听为大娘道来。想儿的娘亲，与为大娘的不和，不该用杯药茶，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要将为大娘的害死。不想儿的娘舅，来在家中，将这杯药茶吞吃腹内，一霎"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "时七孔流血，一命身亡。儿的娘亲一见儿的母舅身死，一计不成，又生二计。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去至公堂，击鼓鸣冤，反说为大娘的害死，将为大娘屈打成招，问成死罪，下"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "入监牢。我儿闻知，去至监牢，搭救为大娘的性命，替为大娘的一死。多亏新"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "任老爷，尚未上任，如此我儿，你情愿替为大娘的认罪，将为大娘放出监牢，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将我的儿收入监内。为大娘回得家去，闻听人言，我儿今日出斩，为大娘打来"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "几杯浊酒，买来几文纸钱，以表我儿搭救大娘的情肠，儿要喝上几杯。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张浪子喝酒，吐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张浪子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吃不下了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吃不下了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "郎二虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老太太，我也吃上几杯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥，你也要吃上几杯？"
        },
        {
          "character": "郎二虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿死在阴曹，你要多多照应。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（郎二虎吃酒，吐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朗二虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吃不下了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你也吃不下了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿呀，为娘打来几文纸钱，与你焚化。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿！儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本当为大娘的拜儿几拜，怎奈是大不拜小，只恐我儿消受不起，为大娘的望空"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一拜也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "眼望法场深深拜，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拜上我儿听开怀："
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王氏下。王清天上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王清天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "时辰可到？"
        },
        {
          "character": "二刽子手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "时辰已到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王清天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将郎二虎开刀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朗二虎下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二刽子手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二刽子手同斩朗二虎。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王清天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将浪子开刀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "太监",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "圣旨下！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（太监上。王清天迎接。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "圣旨下，跪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王清天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听宣读。诏曰：今有药茶一案，律应斩首。后宫娘娘讲情，只可以赦，不可以"
        },
        {
          "character": "太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "斩。圣意读罢，望诏谢恩哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王清天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "犯人在哪儿哪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王清天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在席棚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "让我瞧瞧。不是女人么，怎么是个男人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王清天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乃前官所断。"
        },
        {
          "character": "太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你倒推了个干净。"
        },
        {
          "character": "太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩子们！将他给我背进宫去！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（太监背张浪子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王清天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掩门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
