    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "张浪子",
        "王氏"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张浪子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张浪子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张浪子",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "法场得活命，死去又复生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张浪子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我，张浪子。只因我妈跟我大娘不和，要把我大娘害死。我妈将茶下上毒药，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张浪子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "给我大娘喝，我大娘不喝。不想我娘舅来到家中，可就把这杯药茶喝了。吃下"
        },
        {
          "character": "张浪子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去七窍流血，可就死啦。我妈一见我娘舅死啦，去至公堂击鼓鸣冤，反说我大"
        },
        {
          "character": "张浪子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娘害死我娘舅，将我大娘屈打成招，问成死罪。我想大娘平日待我不错，不免"
        },
        {
          "character": "张浪子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去至监牢，替换我大娘一死。可巧前官升走，新官尚未上任。这么我就去拉三"
        },
        {
          "character": "张浪子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "班衙役，与我很有交情，我说你们将我大娘放出，我情愿替我大娘一死。这么"
        },
        {
          "character": "张浪子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就把我大娘放出，将我收在监里。今日是我出斩之日，我大娘打来酒饭，前来"
        },
        {
          "character": "张浪子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祭奠我来啦。正要杀我的时候，来了一群公公，将我背进宫去。瞧见我兄弟得"
        },
        {
          "character": "张浪子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "了进宝状元。我姐姐封为郡主。我出来接我大娘享享福。不免去至法场等候。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张浪子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我大娘一定要收拾我的尸首来。呦呵，好小子郎二虎，我大娘打酒你也要吃，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张浪子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在你死啦，我打你两下。慢着，人死不记仇，我来抹你点人血。远远望见我"
        },
        {
          "character": "张浪子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大娘来也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王氏上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忽听大炮响一声，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我收浪子死尸临。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
